@PaulAngus it looks like some merge got things a bit wonky. I've just looked at the commit which has changes in the db migration file. One thing that I would like to point out is that it is missing guest-os to hypervisor mapping. You can see those here which I added for XenServer 7

https://github.com/apache/cloudstack/pull/1711/commits/eabf862ba9751bcdbe18a6cc9b91f2ae48472cab#diff-ddcf54a00161e216f9bd9f98a7bbad15

For the most part, they should be the same for XenServer 7.1 and 7.2 as well. @pdion891  had added them for 7.1
